ACTIVE
================================================================================
LUDUZO autonomous build — HARD MODE (ThinkerThinker A23)

The FIRST LINE of this file is the control switch, read by the Stop hook
(.claude/hooks/build-continue-guard.mjs):

  • ACTIVE  → the agent may NOT stop. Every attempt to end a turn is blocked and
             the agent is told to keep building. There is no self-authorized stop.

  • STOP    → the founder's command. The agent is allowed to stop.
             (HALT / STAND DOWN / END / DONE / CEASE also work.)

TO STOP THE BUILD (founder command only), do ONE of:
  1. change the first line above from  ACTIVE  to  STOP , or
  2. delete this file.

Nothing else — not "hard-blocked", not "nothing buildable", not "waiting on you" —
lets the agent stop. Only your command via this file.
================================================================================
